{"tid":1026501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]2月17賽馬日”相中好友”戰死沙田馬場","createTime":"2019-02-18T07:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T07:38:33.000Z","uid":236536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"274008c6d6cbe8c808578e554ece9c24c2535699","tid":1026501,"uid":236536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ay2eAno.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fay2eAno.png&h=3113b2ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n灰馬相中好友在跑道中央倒地不起<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gt6fjO7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGt6fjO7.png&h=7d893a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在工作人員到達前，相中好友已毫無動靜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WSVjPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WSVjPb.png&h=f2796f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工作人員圍上黑布處理相中好友<br />\n<br />\n今日（17日）沙田馬場舉行三場大賽，各項冠軍亦已經名花有主，不過第八場三班草地1800米，出現豬年首宗馬圈不幸事故。<br />\n<br />\n徐雨石馬房「相中好友」在客串騎師夏禮賢胯下，早段已不斷受催策，上到較前位置。轉入直路後，馬匹卻開始收慢，更在最後200米附近收停，騎師夏禮賢即時落馬，但「相中好友」在其他工作人員抵達前，已躺在草地跑道上動也不動。<br />\n<br />\n馬會員工即時將「相中好友」圍上黑布，拖上運馬車送走，相信已返魂乏術。<br />\n<br />\n從賽事片段可見「相中好友」收慢時腳部動作無不妥，今次事故或基於心臟問題。愛爾蘭四歲自購灰馬「相中好友」的馬主是朱鴻鈞與朱惟儉，亦為他們首匹在港賽駒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20190217/59270966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F59270966&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=99292a3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F59270966&h=383ffbae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20190217/59270966</a>"},{"pid":"e1b58d0b3d3854ca25283a176cb6ab2b85e6f0a6","tid":1026501,"uid":236536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"馬馬rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe8f3868cdac331ebd80bf5389b300eebb2fc00","tid":1026501,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a287144335e0a442c5051c997b1b27e659dfbbf3","tid":1026501,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"操撚死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84bb8b1ef045dc9765373a0be5874edf5b2e7dc","tid":1026501,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"愛護動物撚全面進場"},{"pid":"28e7f0c0e7c1d5cde57b3ac6c1f8a3b65a0f4a25","tid":1026501,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"圍上黑布係處理個騎師<br />\n隻馬無人理"},{"pid":"2a3deb05806f75e2e7ece665928d530eac9c3897","tid":1026501,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"隻馬比人谷爆咗？<br />\n好慘"},{"pid":"4f13f910c8e3db4fa30c21a58e6d7a519dc6dec8","tid":1026501,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"告馬會馬主練馬師騎師虐畜"},{"pid":"321c79208b7bfd61788e94accd4111559e3b4eee","tid":1026501,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3947c6f18c6a622d248fedcd9747edaf9c2d652c","tid":1026501,"uid":139228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:31:01.000Z","msg":"反虐畜撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865bc11207591a498d032ef664371e5f3b18f6d5","tid":1026501,"uid":209301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:32:37.000Z","m